Class CycAssertTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.AbstractKbTool
      • com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool.CycAssertTool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AssertTool

    public class CycAssertTool
extends AbstractKbTool
implements AssertTool
    Tools for asserting facts to the Cyc KB. To unassert facts from the Cyc KB, use the CycUnassertTool. To perform simple tasks, like constant creation or renaming, use the CycObjectTool.
    See Also:
    CycUnassertTool, CycObjectTool
